<p><a href="/wiki/Internal_capsule" title="Internal capsule">Internal capsule</a> (<a href="/wiki/Anterior_limb_of_internal_capsule" title="Anterior limb of internal capsule">Anterior limb</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Genu_of_internal_capsule" title="Genu of internal capsule">Genu</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Posterior_limb_of_internal_capsule" title="Posterior limb of internal capsule">Posterior limb</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Corona_radiata" title="Corona radiata">Corona radiata</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/External_capsule" title="External capsule">External capsule</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lamina_terminalis" title="Lamina terminalis">Lamina terminalis</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Extreme_capsule" title="Extreme capsule">Extreme capsule</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Semioval_center" title="Semioval center">Semioval center</a></p>
